resources.description:
Updates a list of recipes for the given plant. If the hasBeenReleased property is set to true, then the following fields are updated:
 - the description, current version, quantity validation, entry phase ID, custom values, and operation groups fields of a recipe;
 - the description, entry, work center, production process ID fields of a recipe phase;
 - the weight relevant field of a recipe operation phase;
 - the tolerance over and under fields of a recipe phase component.

