resources.description:
Updates a list of routings for the given plant. If the hasBeenReleased property is set to true, then the following fields are updated:
 - the description, current version, quantity validation, entry routing step ID, custom values, and routing operation groups fields of a routing;
 - the description, entry, work center, production process ID fields of a routing step;
 - the weight relevant field of a routing operation step;
 - the tolerance over and under fields of a routing step component.

